name: Sunny Aggarwal
description: Sunny Aggarwal is the Co-Founder of Osmosis, the premier interchain DEX and DeFi hub for the Cosmos ecosystem and beyond. At Tendermint, Sunny served as a Core Developer of the Cosmos SDK, and helped to develop and launch Cosmos and IBC. Sunny then built Osmosis on this foundation, to deliver an appchain and DEX that rivals even the most robust centralized exchanges.
